Sadly, this contains multiple viruses (virii?).  The setup.exe is clean, but the BIN files contain encrypted viruses.  Norton Internet Security 2012 caught them as they were being extracted, thankfully.  A virus scan will not detect anything, until you run setup.exe, then, if your AV is good enough, you will see the viruses in the files.
